{"tid":1126383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿小學時被揶揄「廢紙」　返母校用鈔票摑老師臉　23歲男自簽守行為","createTime":"2019-04-26T10:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T05:57:30.000Z","uid":34222,"like":289,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"6fab4a55ebc73cea11587c5af5b298ff90a5d022","tid":1126383,"uid":34222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:49:56.000Z","msg":"23歲男子稱讀小學時不滿被老師比喻為「回收箱入面嘅藍廢紙」，一直耿耿於懷，去年重返母校外斥責該老師，更兩度用鈔票摑打對方臉孔。男生今在西九龍裁判法院承認一項「襲擊致造成身體傷害罪」，被判以自簽2000元守行為1年，並賠償事主1000元、支付300元訟費。<br />\n<br />\n被告莊洋洋（23歲）今承認，去年9月20日在葵涌慈幼葉漢小學外襲擊李家偉，對對方造成身體傷害。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官聽畢案情後曾問被告，為何用鈔票拍打別人臉部。被告回應稱，「佢（案中事主）比喻我係回收箱入面嘅藍廢紙」。裁判官聞言表示，一個人是否受人尊重，不是視乎掙多少錢，又形容被告「咁樣做好侮辱」。<br />\n<br />\n案情指出，被告讀小學時，曾因學業不佳被事主懲罰，令他耿耿於懷。至去年9月，被告在母校外情緒激動斥責事主，並用胸口撞撃事主3次，更從銀包取出11張港元和人民幣鈔票，兩度用鈔票摑打事主臉孔。被告又用手兩度抓住事主的衣領，導致對方頸部輕微擦傷。<br />\n<br />\n事主其他同事見狀報警，被告在警誡下表示「我只係同佢嘈，我冇打過佢」，到其後在錄影會面時指出，自己小學時因學業不佳遭事主懲罰，故透過撞撃及用鈔票摑打對方，來表達不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190426/s00001/1556274696090/%e4%b8%8d%e6%bb%bf%e5%b0%8f%e5%ad%b8%e6%99%82%e8%a2%ab%e6%8f%b6%e6%8f%84%e3%80%8c%e5%bb%a2%e7%b4%99%e3%80%8d-%e8%bf%94%e6%af%8d%e6%a0%a1%e7%94%a8%e9%88%94%e7%a5%a8%e6%91%91%e8%80%81%e5%b8%ab%e8%87%89-23%e6%ad%b2%e7%94%b7%e8%87%aa%e7%b0%bd%e5%ae%88%e8%a1%8c%e7%82%ba\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190426%2Fs00001%2F1556274696090%2F%25e4%25b8%258d%25e6%25bb%25bf%25e5%25b0%258f%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e6%2599%2582%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258f%25b6%25e6%258f%2584%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%25bb%25a2%25e7%25b4%2599%25e3%2580%258d-%25e8%25bf%2594%25e6%25af%258d%25e6%25a0%25a1%25e7%2594%25a8%25e9%2588%2594%25e7%25a5%25a8%25e6%2591%2591%25e8%2580%2581%25e5%25b8%25ab%25e8%2587%2589-23%25e6%25ad%25b2%25e7%2594%25b7%25e8%2587%25aa%25e7%25b0%25bd%25e5%25ae%2588%25e8%25a1%258c%25e7%2582%25ba&d=tLsEO8KpRnvfRHW%2FlT3TjhPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=b4c48139\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190426%2Fs00001%2F1556274696090%2F%25e4%25b8%258d%25e6%25bb%25bf%25e5%25b0%258f%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e6%2599%2582%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258f%25b6%25e6%258f%2584%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%25bb%25a2%25e7%25b4%2599%25e3%2580%258d-%25e8%25bf%2594%25e6%25af%258d%25e6%25a0%25a1%25e7%2594%25a8%25e9%2588%2594%25e7%25a5%25a8%25e6%2591%2591%25e8%2580%2581%25e5%25b8%25ab%25e8%2587%2589-23%25e6%25ad%25b2%25e7%2594%25b7%25e8%2587%25aa%25e7%25b0%25bd%25e5%25ae%2588%25e8%25a1%258c%25e7%2582%25ba&h=b4032bf2\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190426/s00001/1556274696090/%e4%b8%8d%e6%bb%bf%e5%b0%8f%e5%ad%b8%e6%99%82%e8%a2%ab%e6%8f%b6%e6%8f%84%e3%80%8c%e5%bb%a2%e7%b4%99%e3%80%8d-%e8%bf%94%e6%af%8d%e6%a0%a1%e7%94%a8%e9%88%94%e7%a5%a8%e6%91%91%e8%80%81%e5%b8%ab%e8%87%89-23%e6%ad%b2%e7%94%b7%e8%87%aa%e7%b0%bd%e5%ae%88%e8%a1%8c%e7%82%ba</a>"},{"pid":"f2af5e719765069360417eaf51dd7807c5b25ff1","tid":1126383,"uid":201237,"like":89,"dislike":2,"score":87,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:51:32.000Z","msg":"莊洋洋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩名嚟"},{"pid":"29a21b028e696e7f2a00959efbbedbc7eccaf157","tid":1126383,"uid":45684,"like":218,"dislike":2,"score":216,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:51:49.000Z","msg":"個教畜侮辱人就得"},{"pid":"3ca680df067758b4229b5d44c21d717b5cce09e6","tid":1126383,"uid":141151,"like":279,"dislike":2,"score":277,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:52:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>又形容被告「咁樣做好侮辱」。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n人地就係要咁對返老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796f4ace156b8d6608ea38085bde1e17daab2c9a","tid":1126383,"uid":8636,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"quote":{"pid":"f2af5e71976